metadata.name: INTROSPECTION
metadata.description:
Mxse I: 



Me, that I’m always overthinking my own ethics and look through myself with a magnifying glass. 

Constantly searching for a reconciliation in vain. 

Have realised that I only can end this war, by ending it first with myself.

6300 x 6300

Digital painting by Habiba Green
